    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and runs like a dream! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready for its next adventure with you. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. Come check it out!",
