    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a high-revving valvetrain that has recently undergone a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and VANOS system refresh. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement plates to mitigate common floor pan fatigue, and the suspension maintains its precision thanks to updated bushings and Bilstein dampers. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains robust, offering the analog tactile feedback and linear power delivery that defines this era of M-engineering.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
