    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and remains in impressive condition both inside and out. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only the minor road wear you would expect from a carefully driven car. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and remarkably clean; the premium upholstery shows minimal wear, and every feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the navigation system\u2014functions exactly as it should. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having benefited from regular oil changes and all scheduled maintenance intervals. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and sits on a set of high-quality tires with significant tread life remaining. This is a reliable, turn-key example that offers a balanced blend of performance and comfort for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
