      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Boasting a well-documented service history and a robust mechanical profile, the automobile delivers a refined driving experience characterized by both reliability and performance. The interior remains in impressive order, complementing a clean exterior that reflects a high standard of previous ownership. We invite you to experience the enduring quality and sophisticated engineering of this exceptional unit.",
