      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in wonderful shape, ready for plenty more adventures! It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so you\u2019re getting a solid vehicle that\u2019s super comfortable and drives like a dream. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable set of wheels that feels just right, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
